            'requestParamsDescription' => '## CallBack'."\n"
                .'通过用户传入的CallbackUrl，回调用户的内容，示例如下所示：'."\n"
                ."\n"
                .'```'."\n"
                .'Request:'."\n"
                ."\n"
                .'POST /callbackURL'."\n"
                ."\n"
                .'Body'."\n"
                .'application/json'."\n"
                ."\n"
                .'{'."\n"
                .'    "MsgId": "消息ID",'."\n"
